These files are for printing a case for The Shutter Tester.
Print one TheShutterTesterBox and one ShutterTesterBottom.

There is a choice of three rear panels, either without legends,
with engraveved legends 

or the third option using flush text of a different colour.
This file will require changingsettings in your slicer, to print the 
text first, then change colour for printing the main rear part.

Finallythere is a blanking piece for unused holes.
